<h1 style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 36px; color: #000000;">
  Hi <%= recipient_first_name %>,
</h1>

<p style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #374151;">
  Thanks for signing up. Please confirm your email address by clicking the button below:
</p>

<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
  <tr>
    <td>
      <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        <tr>
          <td align="center" style="border-radius: 6px;" bgcolor="#000000">
            <a href="<%= @confirm_url %>" target="_blank" style="font-size: 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px 32px; border: 1px solid #000000; display: inline-block; font-weight: 500;">
              Confirm my email
            </a>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="margin: 32px 0 0 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; color: #6b7280;">
  If you didn't create an account, you can ignore this email.
</p>
